column38: It's safer for me to know the passwords, than just depend on some app. I'm afraid that if I start changing passwords to harder ones, that one day I'll forget the password to log in in the Password Saver itself. I prefer just to memorize something that I easily can think of, rather than memorizing random numbers or letters and symbols. I also use the IOS cloud password saver, and I mostly use these apps, just so I can quickly log in, rather than just typing the password every single time if my browsers forget them.
